                <subtitle>China’s Investors-Backed Tech</subtitle>
                <chapter>
                  <paragraph>China’s rich and wealthy are pouring money into start-up
                    tech ventures in the absence of many other profitable investiment opportunities.
                    Venture capital investments into China’s technology startups more than doubled
                    to $32.2b in 2015, with $4.7b of investments so far this year.</paragraph>
